M||name|copywriting
M||desc|>-
M||tx|When the us wants to write, rewrite, or improve mk cp for any page — inc homepage, landing pages, pricing pages, feature pages, abt pages, or pd pages. Also use when the us says "write cp for," "improve this cp," "rewrite this page," "mk cp," "hl help," "CTA cp," "value proposition," "tagline," "subheadline," "hero section cp," "above the fold," "this cp is weak," "make this more compelling," or "help me describe my pd." Use this whenever someone is working on website text that needs to persuade or convert. For em cp, see em-sequence. For popup cp, see popup-cro. For editing existing cp, see cp-editing.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||plat|[]
M||meta|
M||herm|
