M|Abov|it|Expands on hl
M|Abov|it|Adds specificity
M|Abov|it|1-2 sentences max
M|Abov|tx|**Primary CTA**
M|Abov|it|Action-oriented button text
M|Abov|- Co|"Start Free Trial" > "Sign Up"
